{"tid":2239967,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"近6萬人聯署撐利君雅 前港台監製斥事件罕見旨在殺雞儆猴","createTime":"2020-10-12T10:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T11:04:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e10c3d155dbc61bb5869f6d2432594c7f3d68747","tid":2239967,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"「撐公共廣播運動」今午（12日）到港台遞交聯署信，聲援利君雅。聯署由9月底至上周末，共獲得接近5.9萬人簽名支持。前港台電視部公共事務組監製麥麗晶形容事件「絕無僅有」，投訴指利君雅提問大聲、對某人無禮貌等，並不在主管對員工的評核標準內。據她所知，利君雅的工作表現非常好，批評今次事件目的是貶低利君雅的專業水平，及達致殺雞儆猴，「所有新聞同事斯斯文文、陰聲細氣，有嘢就唔好問啦咁樣」，令新聞界及港台作為公共廣播機構應有的角色受損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/ALLUF7ANDJFOPJSL7ZI5BKMCPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FALLUF7ANDJFOPJSL7ZI5BKMCPY%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBS8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=fa16eef4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FALLUF7ANDJFOPJSL7ZI5BKMCPY%2F&h=2ee5e9cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/ALLUF7ANDJFOPJSL7ZI5BKMCPY/</a>"},{"pid":"45f93a07d205572122e023688769562217ce0c74","tid":2239967,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399b87f9adf9fbc14012741cf13a713f0a1c460b","tid":2239967,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45f93a07d205572122e023688769562217ce0c74","tid":2239967,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c